## API path alignment check

All fetch calls in index.html use paths that exactly match the blueprint routes:
- `/login` -> POST /api/edtech/login
- `/student` -> GET /api/edtech/student
- `/grades` -> GET /api/edtech/grades
- `/grades/<id>` -> PATCH /api/edtech/grades/<id>
- `/activities` -> GET/POST /api/edtech/activities
- `/messages` -> GET/POST /api/edtech/messages
- `/messages/read-all` -> PATCH /api/edtech/messages/read-all
- `/messages/unread-count` -> GET /api/edtech/messages/unread-count

---

